list.abstract: hundred（英 [ˈhʌndrəd]，美 [ˈhʌndrəd]），英语单词。作为数词为一百；世纪；一百岁。作为名词为百户邑。短语搭配有hundreds of，one hundred，five hundred。例句：Carl sold it for twenty-two hundred francs.（Carl以2200法郎卖掉了它。） 近义词有lots of，sea，host。

《Hundred百武装战记》（ハンドレッド）是日本轻小说家箕崎准著作，插画家大熊猫介负责插画，GA文库所属的轻小说。2015年10月22日，繁体中文版由尖端出版社代理发行。 该小说讲述了少年如月隼人为弄清梦中的少女的真面目，入学了海上学园都市舰《Little garden》，并以成为能够使用hundred的《武艺者（slayer）》为目标的故事。 2016年4月4日，根据该小说改编的动画同名《Hundred百武装战记》在日本播出。

yingyinNormal.en: How ridiculous is he? A hundred.
yingyinNormal.zh: 这家伙有多奇怪啊。百分百。

yingyinNormal.en: Here's a hundred bucks to start with.
yingyinNormal.zh: 开始就先给你一百块吧。

yingyinNormal.en: Unless, of course, the piece of paper was a hundred dollar bill.
yingyinNormal.zh: 除非那张纸是一张百元大钞。

yingyinNormal.en: Unless, of course, the piece of paper was a hundred dollar bill.
yingyinNormal.zh: 除非那张纸是一张百元大钞。

yingyinNormal.en: You do owe me so much. You owe me three thousand, four hundred…
yingyinNormal.zh: 你本来就欠我的，你欠我3千4百…

yingyinNormal.en: We're not playing. This is real work. We're going to be hundred-aires.
yingyinNormal.zh: 我们这不是玩儿，这是正事。我们就要成为百-富翁咯。

yingyinNormal.en: I am Hundred Eyes. I am kept here to train the Khan's sons, his nobles, his pets.
yingyinNormal.zh: 我是百眼，我负责训练大汗的儿子，他的贵族，他的宠物。

yingyinNormal.en: What makes a hundred dollar bill valuable, on the other hand, is how many or few of them are around.
yingyinNormal.zh: 而百元钞票的价值所在则是取决于它们数量的多寡。

yingyinNormal.en: What makes a hundred dollar bill valuable, on the other hand, is how many or few of them are around.
yingyinNormal.zh: 而百元钞票的价值所在则是取决于它们数量的多寡。

yingyinNormal.en: So why doesn't the Fed just decide to print infinite hundred dollar bills to make everyone happy and rich?
yingyinNormal.zh: 那联准会怎么不干脆印制无数的百元大钞让大家有钱又开心？

yingyinNormal.en: So why doesn't the Fed just decide to print infinite hundred dollar bills to make everyone happy and rich?
yingyinNormal.zh: 那联准会怎么不干脆印制无数的百元大钞让大家有钱又开心？

yingyinNormal.en: A hundred dollar bill is printed by the government and designated as official currency, while other pieces of paper are not.
yingyinNormal.zh: 百元钞票是政府印制的是官方货币，但其他纸张不是。

yingyinNormal.en: A hundred dollar bill is printed by the government and designated as official currency, while other pieces of paper are not.
yingyinNormal.zh: 百元钞票是政府印制的是官方货币，但其他纸张不是。

yingyinNormal.en: In few hundred years, science has taken us farther in understanding the universe, than the religion has in ten thousand.
yingyinNormal.zh: 百年间科学引领我们了解宇宙的深度，就已经远超宗教几千年的成果。

yingyinNormal.en: Okay, so that's another five hundred. Five hundred and five hundred, that's…
yingyinNormal.zh: 好吧，再加五百块，五百加五百是…

yingyinNormal.en: Are you saying you killed a hundred people to make this?
yingyinNormal.zh: 你杀了一百人用来制造这个？

yingyinNormal.en: I don't know, five hundred dollars? Okay, five hundred dollars. What else? Well, then there was the second set, the infamous booger head shots.
yingyinNormal.zh: 我不知道，五百块。好吧，五百块，还有呢？还有第二组沙龙照，可怕的“怪物”大头照。

yingyinNormal.en: You agree with this? Hundred percent. You want this door closed?
yingyinNormal.zh: 你没意见吧。百分之百，要我带上门吗？

yingyinNormal.en: This fifteen hundred year old fusion of kung fu and religion is kept alive by the neat order of monks that inspired over a hundred martial arts movies.
yingyinNormal.zh: 功夫和宗教的融合，一千五百年来在僧人的有序领导下保持着勃勃生机，这促进了一百多部功夫电影的诞生。

yingyinNormal.en: I'm just saying, don't freak out until you're a hundred percent sure.
yingyinNormal.zh: 我是说没有百分之百确定前，别大惊小怪。

word_usage.usage:
hundred前面若有具体的数词修饰,hundred要用原形，而hundreds of表示不确切的数字，意为“数百的”。
如：two hundred cows 两百头奶牛,hundreds of cows数百头奶牛。
